author: Ashleigh Raper
title: While the focus was on Bondi Beach, coronavirus was silently spreading elsewhere
description: Shocking scenes of people sunning themselves at Bondi Beach went viral last Friday, but the most concerning coronavirus development was happening on a cruise ship at Circular Quay.
